Independent Directors

GB-BDC's independent board members each possess three decades of hands-on experience in the capital markets, having worked at leading Wall Street investment banks in fixed income, research, credit analysis, investment banking and principal investing capacities, as well as serving in leadership positions and on boards of directors at prominent public and private companies.




 


