2016 Press Releases





 


March 16, 2016
 
		Griffin-Benefit Street Partners BDC Corp. Announces: Suspension of Offering Pending Evaluation of Fund Structure Alternatives and Concurrent Suspension of Distribution Reinvestment Plan

The Board of Directors of Griffin-Benefit Street Partners BDC Corp. ("GB-BDC") has determined it is in the best interest of GB-BDC and its stockholders to suspend the continuous public offering of GB-BDC's common stock under its prospectus, dated December 10, 2015.












